TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT /*+ PARALLEL(sf, 4) */ DISTINCT m.MEME_CK, g.GRGR_ID, g.GRGR_CK, a.SBAD_COUNTY, SUBSTR(g.GRGR_ID,1,2) AS PLAN_STATE, e.MEPE_EFF_DT, e.MEPE_TERM_DT, e.MEPE_ELIG_IND, m.MEME_HICN, m.SBSB_CK, sf.SF_ID_ACCT, s.SBSB_ID, e.CSCS_ID, e.CSPI_ID, e.PDPD_ID, m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM FACETS.CMC_MEME_MEMBER m INNER JOIN FACETS.CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND SUBSTR(GRGR_ID, 1,5) = 'VA'||'MCD' INNER JOIN AGP.SF_DSNP_VA_ENROLL d ON m.MEME_MEDCD_NO = d.MEDICAID_NUMBER INNER JOIN FACETS.CMC_SBSB_SUBSC s ON m.SBSB_CK = s.SBSB_CK INNER JOIN FACETS.CMC_SBAD_ADDR a ON m.SBSB_CK = a.SBSB_CK AND M.SBAD_TYPE_HOME = A.SBAD_TYPE INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK INNER JOIN agp.SFDC_MEMBER sf ON SUBSTR(g.GRGR_ID,1,2)||'MCD'|| TRIM(m.MEME_MEDCD_NO) = sf.MBR_EXT_ID AND m.MEME_CK = sf.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(ex.MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG ex WHERE ex.MEME_CK = E.MEME_CK AND ex.MEPE_EFF_DT < sysdate ) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND sf.MEME_CK <> 'ael' AND sf.MEME_CK <> 'NA' /* handling bad data */
